xd:platformInfo.xd:description: Basic platform targeting the ZC706 board, which includes 1GB of DDR3 for the Processing System, 1GB DDR3 for the Programmable Logic, 2x16MB Quad-SPI Flash and an SDIO card interface. More information at https://www.xilinx.com/products/boards-and-kits/ek-z7-zc706-g.html
